托利斯在[[2006年世界盃足球賽|2006年世界盃]]後，拒絕在[[2005–06赛季西班牙足球甲级联赛|2005–06賽季]]完結後加盟切爾西。<ref>{{Cite news|first=Tom|last=Adams|title='Flattered' Villa to stay with Che|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11667/2404638/flattered-villa-to-stay-with-che|publisher=天空體育|date=2007-02-06|accessdate=2014-08-05|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125235825/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11667/2404638/flattered-villa-to-stay-with-che|dead-url=no}}</ref> 托雷斯在[[2006–07赛季西班牙足球甲级联赛|2006–07賽季]]打進14球。<ref name="Torres"/> 英格蘭的媒體紛紛報導他成為[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]的主要引援目標，<ref>{{Cite news|first=David|last=Prentice|title=Torres is Reds' number one target|url=http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0500liverpoolfc/0100news/tm_headline=torres-is-reds%2D-number-one-target%26method=full%26objectid=19326444%26siteid=50061-name_page.html|newspaper=Liverpool Echo|date=2007-06-20|accessdate=2007-06-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603224454/http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0500liverpoolfc/0100news/tm_headline=torres-is-reds--number-one-target%26method=full%26objectid=19326444%26siteid=50061-name_page.html|archivedate=2013-06-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>但塞雷索稱：「我們沒有收到任何從利物浦或任何其他俱樂部的報價」。<ref name="No Reds offer for Torres">{{Cite news| title = No Reds offer for Torres| url = http://www.thedailystar.net/2007/06/27/d70627043553.htm| newspaper = The Daily Star| location = Dhaka| date = 2007-06-27| accessdate = 2010-06-20| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024102246/http://www.thedailystar.net/2007/06/27/d70627043553.htm| archivedate = 2012-10-24| dead-url = no}}</ref> 無論如何，在數天後，媒體表示馬競已經同意利物浦有關托雷斯的報價，而報價高達2,500萬歐元再附上[[路易斯·哈维尔·加西亚·桑斯|路易斯·加西亚]]。<ref name="Garcia the key as Liverpool step up pursuit of Torres">{{Cite news|first=Oliver|last=Kay|title=Garcia the key as Liverpool step up pursuit of Torres|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/liverpool/article1996591.ece|newspaper=The Times|date=2007-06-28|accessdate=2010-06-20|location=London|archive-date=2011-09-18|archive-url=https://archive.today/20110918062132/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/liverpool/article1996591.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同時，馬德里競技已為托利斯離隊作出準備，並於6月30日從[[比利亞雷阿爾足球俱樂部|比利亞雷阿爾]]簽入前鋒[[迪亞高·科蘭|迪亞高·科蘭]]。<ref name="Liverpool complete Torres signing">{{Cite news|title=Liverpool complete Torres signing|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/6239286.stm|publisher=BBC體育|date=2007-07-04|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2019-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529195319/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/6239286.stm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同年7月2日，媒體表示托雷斯已經縮短自己的假期並飛返馬德里再前往利物浦。<ref name="Torres' £27m Liverpool deal">{{Cite news|first=Charles|last=Carrick|title=Torres' £27m Liverpool deal|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2316106/Torres-27m-Liverpool-deal.html|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|date=2007-06-30|accessdate=2011-05-18|location=London|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017214739/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2316106/Torres-27m-Liverpool-deal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 接下來的數天，托雷斯最終在利物浦Melwood訓練基地通過體測。<ref name="Liverpool wrap up record Torres transfer">{{Cite news|title=Liverpool wrap up record Torres transfer|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2007/jul/04/newsstory.sport3|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2007-07-04|accessdate=2014-08-05|location=London|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018065439/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2007/jul/04/newsstory.sport3|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他在與利物浦簽下六年合約前，在7月4日於馬德里舉行記者招待會向馬競一眾球迷道別。<ref name="Liverpool wrap up record Torres transfer"/> 而這次轉會費是利物浦史上最高。<ref name="Liverpool complete Torres signing"/> 在2008年3月，[[領隊_(足球)|主教練]][[拉法埃尔·贝尼特斯|拉法埃尔·贝尼特斯]] 在接受[[泰晤士報|泰晤士報]]的訪問時表示，雖然加西亞同時轉會到馬競，但托雷斯的轉會費用只是大約在2,000萬歐元左右。<ref name="Rafael Benitez opens up on transfers, treachery, Torres, titles - and, of course, tinkering">{{Cite ws|first=Guillem|last=Balague|title=Rafael Benitez opens up on transfers, treachery, Torres, titles – and, of course, tinkering|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/liverpool/article3648804.ece|newspaper=泰晤士報|location=倫敦|date=2008-03-31|accessdate=2010-06-20|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20080516025618/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/liverpool/article3648804.ece|archivedate=2008-05-16}}</ref>

=== 利物浦 ===
==== 2007-08球季 ====
托雷斯在2007年8月11日對陣[[阿斯頓維拉足球俱樂部|阿斯頓維拉]]的賽事中首次為利物浦上陣，協助紅軍以2:1擊敗對手。<ref name="Aston Villa 1-2 Liverpool">{{Cite news|first=John|last=Sinnott|title=Aston Villa 1–2 Liverpool|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6931045.stm|publisher=BBC體育|date=2007-08-11|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020064918/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6931045.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 托雷斯在俱樂部1:0擊敗[[圖盧茲足球俱樂部|圖盧茲足球俱樂部]]的[[歐洲冠軍聯賽|歐洲冠軍聯賽]]附加賽中首次在歐冠上陣。他在下半場79分鐘以替補身份上場。.<ref name="Toulouse 0-1 Liverpool">{{Cite news|first=Mandeep|last=Sanghera|title=Toulouse 0–1 Liverpool|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/6941921.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2007-08-15|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017220842/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/6941921.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>托雷斯在2007年8月19日主場對切爾西的賽事中他射入了效力利物浦後首個英超聯賽進球，他在上半場16分鐘便攻破切爾西的大門，協助紅軍最終以1:1戰平對手。<ref name="Liverpool 1-1 Chelsea">{{Cite news|first=Saj|last=Chowdhury|title=Liverpool 1–1 Chelsea|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6941876.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2007-08-19|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018111721/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6941876.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 托雷斯在2007年9月25日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對陣[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]的比賽中做出職業生涯首個[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，所有進球都是在下半場射入，協助紅軍4::2大勝對手。<ref name="Reading 2-4 Liverpool">{{Cite news|first=Andrew|last=McKenzie|title=Reading 2–4 Liverpool|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7008013.stm|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2007-09-25|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020064922/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/7008013.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在歐冠上陣3場後終於在2007年11月28日主場對陣[[波爾圖足球俱樂部|波爾圖]]的歐冠小組賽賽事中打進自己首個歐冠進球兼梅開二度，協助紅軍以4:1大勝對手。<ref name="Liverpool 4-1 FC Porto">{{Cite news| first = John| last = Sinnott| title = Liverpool 4–1 FC Porto| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7110714.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-11-28| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017205418/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7110714.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>
