托雷斯在2008年2月獲選為[[英超每月最佳球員|英超每月最佳球員]]<ref name="Moyes & Torres win monthly awards">{{Cite news| title = Moyes & Torres win monthly awards| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7284223.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-03-07| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018182933/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7284223.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 因為他在該月份上陣4場射入4球，包括在2月23日主場對[[米杜士堡足球會|米德爾斯堡]]的帽子戲法。<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2007/2008"/> 及後托雷斯在3月5日對[[西漢姆聯足球俱樂部|西漢姆聯]]的賽事再次上演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，這也是紅軍60年來第一位連續於主場上演帽子戲法的球員，上一次是在1946年11月由[[傑基·巴爾默|傑基·巴爾默]]（Jackie Balmer）所做出。<ref name="Fernando Torres: My pride at Anfield hat-trick record">{{Cite news| first = Tony| last = Barrett| title = Fernando Torres: My pride at Anfield hat-trick record| url = http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/fernando-torres-pride-anfield-hat-trick-3490568| newspaper = Liverpool Echo| date = 2008-03-06| accessdate = 2014-08-05| archive-date = 2020-10-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201029201453/https://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/fernando-torres-pride-anfield-hat-trick-3490568| dead-url = no}}</ref> 3月15日，利物浦主場2:1反勝[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]，托雷斯在下半場47分鐘以頭槌頂入致勝一球，這亦是他英超第20球進球。自[[罗比·福勒|罗比·福勒]]在[[1995年至1996年英格蘭超級聯賽|1995-96賽季]]打入28球以來，托雷斯是第一個單一賽季聯賽進球超過二十球的利物浦球員。<ref name="Liverpool 2-1 Reading">{{Cite news| first = John| last = May| title = Liverpool 2–1 Reading| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7284959.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-03-15| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017205416/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7284959.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 同年4月，他在歐冠半準決賽次回合對陣[[阿森納足球俱樂部|兵工廠]]再次打進一球，協助紅軍晉級準決賽。<ref name="Liverpool 4-2 Arsenal (agg 5-3)">{{Cite news|first=Andrew|last=McKenzie|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7332209.stm|title=Liverpool 4–2 Arsenal (agg 5–3)|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2008-04-08|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018213507/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7332209.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這次進球也是他在這個賽季各項賽事中的第29球，<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2007/2008"/> 打破了[[迈克尔·欧文|迈克尔·欧文]]所保持的單季進球紀錄。<ref name="Goalscorers for the 2001-2002 season">{{cite web|title=Goalscorers for the 2001–2002 season|url=http://www.lfchistory.net/SeasonArchive/Goalscorers/44|publisher=LFChistory.net|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021083429/https://www.lfchistory.net/SeasonArchive/Goalscorers/44|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在同年4月11日，托雷斯被提名為[[英格蘭PFA足球先生|英格蘭PFA足球先生]]六名侯選人之一，<ref name="Ronaldo tops PFA nominations list">{{Cite news|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7342574.stm|title=Ronaldo tops PFA nominations list|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2008-04-11|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017220844/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7342574.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 最終被[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]球員[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|克里斯蒂亞諾·羅納度]]奪得是次獎項。<ref name="Ronaldo named player of the year">{{Cite news|url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7370319.stm|title=Ronaldo named player of the year|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2008-04-27|accessdate=2011-05-18|archive-date=2019-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531144546/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7370319.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這位西班牙人也被提名為 [[PFA年度最佳青年球員|PFA年度最佳青年球員]]侯選人之一，但獎項最終被兵工廠球員[[塞斯克·法比加斯|塞斯克·法比加斯]]奪得。而托雷斯最終獲選該賽季為[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA年度最佳陣容]]之一。<ref name="Ronaldo named player of the year"/> 5月，不敵羅納度無緣該賽季的[[英格蘭FWA足球先生|英格蘭FWA足球先生]]獎項。<ref name="Ronaldo wins writers' award again">{{Cite news| title = Ronaldo wins writers' award again| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7379586.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-05-02| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018045024/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7379586.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>

2008年5月4日, 托雷斯在利物浦對陣[[曼徹斯特城足球俱樂部|曼城]],的比賽中，在下半場57分鐘打進全賽唯一進球，這也打平了由[[羅傑斯·洪特|羅傑斯·洪特]]（Roger Hunt）所保持的連續在安菲爾德的八場聯賽進球的紀錄。<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2007/2008"/><ref name="Torres equals Hunt record">{{cite news| title = Torres equals Hunt record| url = http://www.football.co.uk/liverpool/torres_equals_hunt_record_264224.shtml| publisher = Football.co.uk| date = 2008-05-05| accessdate = 2014-08-05| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140810073039/http://www.football.co.uk/liverpool/torres_equals_hunt_record_264224.shtml| archivedate = 2014-08-10| dead-url = no}}</ref>在5月11日，利物浦對[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]的英超賽事中，托雷斯打進聯賽第24球，打破了由前曼聯射手[[路德·范尼斯特鲁伊|范尼斯特鲁伊]]保持的外籍球員英超處子賽季的進球紀錄。<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2007/2008"/><ref name="Jose Reina: Fernando Torres will improve">{{Cite news| first = Charlie| last = Caroe| title = Jose Reina: Fernando Torres will improve| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2299624/Jose-Reina-Fernando-Torres-will-improve.html| newspaper = The Daily Telegraph| location = 倫敦| date = 2008-05-06| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018220830/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2299624/Jose-Reina-Fernando-Torres-will-improve.html| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在賽季結束以後共同以24球與[[埃曼纽埃尔·阿德巴约|埃曼纽埃尔·阿德巴约]]完成英超神射手第二名。<ref name="Statistics: top scorers: 2007/2008">{{cite web| title = Statistics: top scorers: 2007/2008| url = http://www.espnfc.com/barclays-premier-league/23/statistics/scorers?season=2007| publisher = ESPN FC| accessdate = 2014-08-05| archive-date = 2020-04-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421045244/http://www.espnfc.com/barclays-premier-league/23/statistics/scorers?season=2007| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯在賽季結束後也受到當地媒體的猜測，指切爾西願意支付五千萬英鎊從利物浦簽下他。但托雷斯表明他只會在很多年後才會離開利物浦。<ref name="Chelsea target Liverpool's Spanish striker Fernando Torres with £50 million bid">{{Cite news| first = Charlie| last = Caroe| title = Chelsea target Liverpool's Spanish striker Fernando Torres with £50 million bid| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2301603/Chelsea-target-Liverpools-Spanish-striker-Fernando-Torres-with-50-million-bid.html| newspaper = 每日電訊報| location = 倫敦| date = 2008-05-26| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018073917/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/2301603/Chelsea-target-Liverpools-Spanish-striker-Fernando-Torres-with-50-million-bid.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Torres pledges long-term future to Reds">{{cite news| title = Torres pledges long-term future to Reds| url = http://www.espnfc.com/story/541317| publisher = ESPN FC| date = 2008-05-31| accessdate = 2014-08-05| archive-date = 2020-04-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421045255/http://www.espnfc.com/story/541317| dead-url = no}}</ref> 時任利物浦持有人[[湯姆·希克斯|湯姆·希克斯]]也否定了托雷斯轉會的想法，他表示他不會允許托雷斯在任何報價上離開俱樂部。<ref name="Hicks laughs off Torres sale talk">{{Cite news| title = Hicks laughs off Torres sale talk| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7459591.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-06-17| accessdate = 2011-05-27| archive-date = 2020-10-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201019235023/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7459591.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>

====2008–09球季====
