托雷斯在[[2008–09賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2008–09賽季]]的首個聯賽進球是在2008年8月16日作客[[新特蘭足球俱樂部|新特蘭]]的時侯所射入。他在離球門25碼打出一記遠射，協助紅軍以1:0擊敗對手。<ref name="Sunderland 0-1 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Jonathan| last = Stevenson| title = Sunderland 0–1 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7551170.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-08-16| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017180136/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7551170.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在0:0戰平阿斯頓維拉的比賽中遭遇了[[腿後腱|腿後腱]]撕裂，這讓他需要休息兩到三個星期。<ref name="Reds confirm Torres injury">{{Cite news| first = Paul| last = Eaton| title = Reds confirm Torres injury| url = http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/latest-news/reds-confirm-torres-injury| publisher = 利物浦足球會| date = 2008-09-01| accessdate = 2012-06-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150403134611/http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/latest-news/reds-confirm-torres-injury| archive-date = 2015-04-03| dead-url = yes}}</ref> 托雷斯在歐洲冠軍聯賽2:1擊敗[[馬賽足球俱樂部|馬賽]]的比賽中重返綠茵賽場以及在2008年9月27日的[[默西賽德郡打吡|默西賽德郡德比]]中打進兩球，協助紅軍以2:0擊敗死敵[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|艾佛頓]]。<ref name="Marseille 1-2 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Mandeep| last = Sanghera| title = Marseille 1–2 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7614129.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-09-16| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020153343/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7614129.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Everton 0-2 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Everton 0–2 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7626897.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-09-27| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020153344/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7626897.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在接下來週末作客曼城的比賽中個人梅開二度，令利物浦在[[曼徹斯特市球場|曼徹斯特市球場]]落後兩球下追平對手，紅軍最後以3:2反勝曼城。<ref name="Man City 2-3 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Mandeep| last = Sanghera| title = Man City 2–3 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7639491.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-10-05| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018111714/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7639491.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 當中第一個進球是利物浦在英超的第一千個進球。<ref name="Man City 2 Liverpool 3">{{Cite news| first = Neil| last = Custis| title = Man City 2 Liverpool 3| url = http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/1769684/Man-City-2-Liverpool-3.html| newspaper = 太陽報| location = 倫敦| date = 2008-10-05| accessdate = 2012-06-20| archive-date = 2012-05-26| archive-url = https://archive.today/20120526092742/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/1769684/Man-City-2-Liverpool-3.html| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯在[[2010年世界盃足球賽|2010年世界盃]][[2010年世界盃外圍賽－歐洲區第五組|外圍賽]]後再次遭遇腿後腱受傷, 也令他需要缺陣三場利物浦的賽事。<ref name="Torres ruled out for '10-15 days'">{{Cite news| title = Torres ruled out for '10–15 days'| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7673163.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-10-16| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018033628/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7673163.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 在2008年10月22日，利物浦在歐冠賽場上客場托雷斯母會馬德里競技，但托雷斯的傷勢導致他無緣是次在比森特·卡爾德隆上演的賽事。<ref name="Atletico Madrid 1-1 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Atletico Madrid 1–1 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7671443.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-10-22| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017225317/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7671443.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 馬競主席恩里克·塞雷索給予他[[重要人物|VIP]]觀眾席給予他欣賞是次賽事，但被他以在默西賽德郡養傷為由而拒絕。<ref name="Fernando Torres puts Chelsea-Liverpool clash ahead of Atletico Madrid return">{{Cite news| first = Mark| last = Ogden| title = Fernando Torres puts Chelsea-Liverpool clash ahead of Atletico Madrid return| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/liverpool/3233126/Fernando-Torres-puts-Chelsea-Liverpool-clash-ahead-of-Atletico-Madrid-return-Football.html| newspaper = The Daily Telegraph| location = 倫敦| date = 2008-10-21| accessdate = 2011-01-21| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017204553/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/liverpool/3233126/Fernando-Torres-puts-Chelsea-Liverpool-clash-ahead-of-Atletico-Madrid-return-Football.html| dead-url = no}}</ref> 2008年10月27日，他被[[國際職業足球員協會|國際職業足球員協會]]提名為2007–08賽季[[國際職業足球員協會#年度世界最佳十一人|世界最佳十一人]]。<ref name="Ronaldo voted FIFPro World Player of the Year">{{Cite news| title = Ronaldo voted FIFPro World Player of the Year| url = http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=767352.html| publisher = UEFA| date = 2008-10-27| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2018-12-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181204162224/https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=767352.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>

托雷斯在2008年11月8日利物浦對陣[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布罗姆维奇]]的比賽中再次為紅軍披甲上陣，他在下半場72分鐘以替補身份上場，協助紅軍以3:0大勝對手。<ref name="Liverpool 3-0 West Brom">{{Cite news| first = Ian| last = Hughes| title = Liverpool 3–0 West Brom| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7697418.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-11-08| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020230719/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7697418.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他也表示他對於最終會回到母會馬競感到興趣，他說:「我不知道我會不會回到那裡退役，但我很樂意回去並完成一些在那裡還沒完成的事。」<ref name="Torres open to Atletico return">{{cite news| title = Torres open to Atletico return| url = http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11669/4476544/torres-open-to-atletico-return| publisher = 天空體育| date = 2008-11-09| accessdate = 2014-08-05| archive-date = 2020-10-25| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201025001115/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11669/4476544/torres-open-to-atletico-return| dead-url = no}}</ref> 但托雷斯在11月利物浦1:0擊敗馬賽的歐冠賽事，賽後被證實拉傷腿筋，令他需再次養傷2至3星期，<ref name="Striker Torres faces new lay-off">{{Cite news| title = Striker Torres faces new lay-off| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7753417.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-11-27| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-10-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021211608/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7753417.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 後來被專家確認需要休息至少四個星期。<ref name="Liverpool hit by Torres setback">{{Cite news| title = Liverpool hit by Torres setback| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7764335.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-12-04| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017204507/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7764335.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯在同年12月被提名為[[國際足協世界足球先生|國際足協世界足球先生]]侯選人之一，<ref name="Ronaldo, Torres up for Fifa award">{{Cite news| title = Ronaldo, Torres up for Fifa award| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7779434.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2008-12-12| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2016-01-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160109084648/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7779434.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 最終他以第三名僅次於羅納度和[[利昂内尔·梅西|利昂内尔·梅西]]。<ref name="Ronaldo collects Fifa world title">{{Cite news| title = Ronaldo collects Fifa world title| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7822115.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-01-12| accessdate = 2009-01-12| archive-date = 2013-08-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130823163643/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/7822115.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯在2009年1月3日以替補身份重返紅軍陣容，更打進一球協助紅軍以2:0擊敗[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯顿]]; 這也是他第一次參加[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]賽事。<ref name="Preston 0-2 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Mark| last = Ashenden| title = Preston 0–2 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7803324.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-01-03| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021211610/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/7803324.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在2009年2月1日對陣切爾西的聯賽梅開二度，協助紅軍2:0擊敗到訪安菲爾德的藍軍。<ref name="Liverpool 2-0 Chelsea">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Liverpool 2–0 Chelsea| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7856404.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-02-01| accessdate = 2009-02-01| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017203956/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7856404.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 儘管托雷斯只在俱樂部效力了了一年半的時間，但他在加盟的短時間內取得了利物浦的成績，令他被'''泰晤士報'''選為「利物浦50名最佳球員」之一。<ref name="The 50 greatest Liverpool players">{{Cite news| first = Tony| last = Evans| title = The 50 greatest Liverpool players| url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/liverpool/article5703041.ece| newspaper = 泰晤士報| location = 倫敦| date = 2009-02-13| accessdate = 2009-02-22| archive-date = 2021-05-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210508062827/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/| dead-url = no}}</ref>

托雷斯在2009年3月10日歐冠16強對陣他的昔日死敵[[皇家馬德里足球俱樂部|皇家馬德里]]，但由於自身腳踝受傷的關係，他為了能夠在比賽中上場而在比賽前注射止痛劑。<ref name="Torres had injection to play against Real Madrid">{{Cite news| first = David| last = Brown| title = Fernando Torres used powers of persuasion to play against Real Madrid| url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/premier_league/liverpool/article5889207.ece| newspaper = 泰晤士報| location = 倫敦| date = 2009-03-11| accessdate = 2009-04-13| archive-date = 2021-02-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227032451/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/| dead-url = no}}</ref>他打進比賽中的首個進球，協助紅軍在主場大勝銀河鑑隊4:0，令利物浦以總比分5:0晉級半準決賽。<ref name="Liverpool 4-0 Real Madrid">{{Cite news| title = Liverpool 4–0 Real Madrid (agg 5–0)| first = Phil| last = McNulty| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7899615.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-03-10| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018111717/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7899615.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 4天後他在[[老特拉福德球场|老特拉福德球场]]作客曼聯的比賽中首發上陣，他在上半場打進一球令紅軍追平比分，而最後紅軍在「[[利曼大戰|雙紅會]]」上以4:1大戰宿敵紅魔。<ref name="Man Utd 1-4 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Man Utd 1–4 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7922069.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-03-14| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201019041728/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7922069.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯在2009年4月被提名為該英超賽季[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA年度最佳陣容]]。<ref name="Giggs earns prestigious PFA award">{{Cite news| title = Giggs earns prestigious PFA award| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8019726.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-04-26| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017204551/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8019726.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 其後他在2009年5月24日對陣熱刺的英超閉幕戰中打進自己在紅軍的第50個進球，這也是他在紅軍的第84場賽事。<ref name="Liverpool 3-1 Tottenham">{{Cite news| first = Oliver| last = Brett| title = Liverpool 3–1 Tottenham| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8048312.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-05-24| accessdate = 2009-05-25| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017225319/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8048312.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>

====2009–10球季====
[[File:Fernando_Torres_1.png|thumb]]
在接下來的賽季，托雷斯同意與利物浦簽訂一份新合約。<ref name="Torres agrees new Liverpool deal">{{Cite news| title = Torres agrees new Liverpool deal| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8072780.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-05-28| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017224251/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8072780.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在同年8月14日正式與紅軍簽下新的合約。.<ref name="Torres signs new Liverpool deal">{{Cite news| title = Torres signs new Liverpool deal| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8201389.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-08-14| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-04-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421045512/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8201389.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 隨着新合約的生效，托雷斯又再延長自己一年的合約，合約將會延長到2013年夏季。<ref name="Torres signs contract extension with Liverpool">{{Cite news| title = Torres signs contract extension with Liverpool| url = http://www.espnfc.com/story/667463| publisher = ESPN FC| date = 2009-08-14| accessdate = 2014-08-05| archive-date = 2020-04-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421045516/http://www.espnfc.com/story/667463| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯在2009年9月19日利物浦對陣[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|西汉姆联]]的賽事中梅開二度，協助紅軍以3:2擊敗對手。而托雷斯的出色表現也令紅軍重返聯賽第三名。<ref name="West Ham 2-3 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Mark| last = Ashenden| title = West Ham 2–3 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8256614.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-09-19| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017191112/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8256614.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 一星期後，他做出了在[[2009–10賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2009–10賽季]]首個帽子戲法，協助紅軍在安菲爾德以6:1大勝[[赫爾城足球俱樂部|赫爾城]]。<ref name="Priceless Fernando Torres slays Hull with a hat-trick show fit for a prince">{{Cite news| first = Andy| last = Hunter| title = Priceless Fernando Torres slays Hull with a hat-trick show fit for a prince| url = http://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/sep/28/liverpool-hull-city-fernando-torres| newspaper = 衛報| location = 倫敦| date = 2009-09-28| accessdate = 2014-08-05| archive-date = 2021-01-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117162845/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/sep/28/liverpool-hull-city-fernando-torres| dead-url = no}}</ref> 由於托雷斯在9月份射入五球的出色表現令他成為了該月份英超最佳球員的以及成為該賽季[[2009–10賽季英格蘭超級聯賽#射手榜|最佳射手]].<ref name="Torres and Ferguson scoop awards">{{Cite news| title = Torres and Ferguson scoop awards| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8287998.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-10-02| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020031420/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8287998.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 2009年10月25日，他在雙紅會中打進一球，協助紅軍以2:0擊敗紅魔，<ref name="Liverpool 2-0 Man Utd">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Liverpool 2–0 Man Utd| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8316379.stm| publisher = BBC Sport體育| date = 2009-10-25| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2013-08-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130823144557/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8316379.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 賽後，主教練貝尼特斯在接受媒體採訪時盛讚托雷斯在場上的表現，他說：「我們都在等待這最後的傳球。當它來到托雷斯的腳下時我們就知道他會破門得分。」<ref name="Benitez hails quality of Torres">{{Cite news| title = Benitez hails quality of Torres| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8325882.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-10-26| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2013-08-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130823173725/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8325882.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>托雷斯在2009年12月再次被提名為世界最佳十一人。<ref name="FIFA/FIFPRO World XI announced">{{cite news| first = Jimmy| last = Leach| title = FIFA/FIFPRO World XI announced| url = http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/fifafifpro-world-xi-announced-1847812.html| newspaper = 獨立報| location = 倫敦| date = 2009-12-22| accessdate = 2014-08-31| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018230754/https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/international/fifafifpro-world-xi-announced-1847812.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>他在2009年12月29日利物浦作客對陣阿斯頓維拉的壓哨進球讓他成為利物浦有史以來最快打進50粒聯賽入球的球員。<ref name="Aston Villa 0-1 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = David| last = Ornstein| title = Aston Villa 0–1 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8428990.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2009-12-29| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018182934/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8428990.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在2010年4月4日1:1作客戰平[[伯明翰城足球俱樂部|伯明翰城]]的比賽中在下半場65分鐘被換下場，原因是貝尼特斯表示托雷斯已經是「筋疲力盡」。<ref name="Rafa Benitez defends his decision to take off Torres">{{Cite news| title = Rafa Benitez defends his decision to take off Torres| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8602891.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2010-04-04| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2016-01-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160109084648/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8602891.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 2010年4月8日，托雷斯在該賽季最後一次上場，他在歐羅霸聯賽對陣[[里斯本與本菲卡體育俱樂部|本菲卡]]的比賽中個人梅開二度，協助紅軍以4:1大勝對手<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2009/2010"/> 但俱樂部並於4月18日宣布，托雷斯因為接受膝蓋手術將錯過本賽季剩下的比賽。<ref name="Liverpool's Fernando Torres out for rest of season">{{Cite news| title = Liverpool's Fernando Torres out for rest of season| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8628770.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2010-04-18| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2013-08-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130823132414/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8628770.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 這也標誌着他在這個賽季各項賽事上陣32場並攻入22球，也是第二次成為隊中最佳射手。<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2009/2010"/>

==== 2010-11球季 ====
[[File:Fernando_Torres_vs_Utrecht.jpg|thumb]]
隨着[[罗伊·霍奇森|霍奇森]]被任命為利物浦的主教練後他表示托雷斯是俱樂部的非賣品，他說:「托雷斯不會被出售，而我們不歡迎任何對於他的報價。我們希望可以留住他。」<ref name="Gerrard and Torres staying at Liverpool - Hodgson">{{Cite news| title = Gerrard and Torres staying at Liverpool – Hodgson| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8829753.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2010-07-16| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017224301/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8829753.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 霍奇森對於有關於托雷斯要離隊的新聞是錯誤的，他駁斥說:他告訴我們他打算在星期一的比賽上陣，他希望儘快重返賽場並展望在下一個賽季繼續為紅軍效力。這就是我所知道的，如果他要離隊我會建議這是錯誤的決定。」<ref name="Hodgson expects Fernando Torres to stay at Liverpool">{{Cite news| title = Hodgson expects Fernando Torres to stay at Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8853856.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2010-07-27| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017224249/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8853856.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>托雷斯在8月3日表示他承諾留在行浦，他說「正如我加盟的第一天，我對俱樂部的承諾和忠誠度和球迷一樣。」<ref name="Striker Fernando Torres committed to Liverpool">{{Cite news| title = Striker Fernando Torres committed to Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8881776.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2010-08-03| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-10-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201021211612/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8881776.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>

他在[[2010–11賽季英格蘭超級聯賽|2010–11賽季]]首次上陣是在2010年8月14日1:1戰平阿森納的揭幕戰，在下半場74分鐘以替補身份上陣。<ref name="Liverpool 1-1 Arsenal">{{Cite news| first = Mandeep| last = Sanghera| title = Liverpool 1–1 Arsenal| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8909559.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2010-08-15| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018142005/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8909559.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 2010年8月29日，利物浦主場迎戰升班馬[[西布朗|-{zh-cn:西布罗姆维奇; zh-hk:西布朗;}-]]，托雷斯於下半場66分鐘射入致勝一球，<ref name="Liverpool 1–0 West Brom">{{Cite news| first = Mandeep| last = Sanghera| title = Liverpool 1–0 West Brom| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8945965.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2010-08-29| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017205421/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/8945965.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 這一球是他在[[晏菲路|-{zh-hans:安菲尔德;zh-hk:晏菲路;zh-tw:安菲爾德;}-]]的第五十個入球，同時亦打破了近4個月的入球荒。<ref name="Torres landmark nets WBA win">{{Cite news| title = Torres landmark nets WBA win| url = http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/latest-news/torres-landmark-nets-wba-win| publisher = Liverpool F.C| date = 2010-08-29| accessdate = 2012-06-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141227231303/http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/latest-news/torres-landmark-nets-wba-win| archive-date = 2014-12-27| dead-url = yes}}</ref>2010年10月24日，托雷斯在俱樂部主場對陣[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布莱克本流浪者]]的比賽中打進致勝一球，協助紅軍以2:1擊敗對手。這也是他自8月來的首個進球。<ref name="Liverpool 2-1 Blackburn">{{Cite news| first = Alistair| last = Magowan| title = Liverpool 2–1 Blackburn| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9107874.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2010-10-24| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020064924/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9107874.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>2010年11月7日，英超第十一輪，利物浦主場對陣榜首的[[車路士|-{zh-hans:切尔西; zh-hk:車路士; zh-tw:切爾西;}-]]，此場賽事托雷斯射入兩個入球，讓托雷斯徹底掃除本賽季開始以來的傷病與狀態低迷，最終利物浦贏2-0，協助利物浦升上積分榜第9位。2011年1月22日，利物浦客場對上[[狼隊|狼隊]]，托雷斯於上半場36'與下半場90+1'各射入一球，加上[[劳尔·梅雷莱斯|-{zh-hans:梅雷莱斯;zh-hk:美利拉斯;zh-tw:美尼利斯;}-]]在50分鐘射入的一球，取得3-0勝利，打破了近30年來客場對陣狼隊不勝以及本赛季此前已經客場五連敗的尷尬記錄，也取得了[[杜格利殊|-{zh-hans:达格利什; zh-hk:杜格利殊;}-]]上任以來的首場勝利，但托雷斯隨即要求轉會，遭利物浦拒絕。<ref name="Wolverhampton 0-3 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Mandeep| last = Sanghera| title = Wolverhampton 0–3 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9365393.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 22 January 2011 accessdate = 18 September 2011| accessdate = 2015-04-04| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018000824/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9365393.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 切尔西 ===
2011年1月27日，切爾西對托雷斯進行4,000萬鎊的報價，但被利物浦所拒絕。<ref name="Chelsea's £40 million bid for Liverpool striker Fernando Torres is an act of desperation">{{Cite news| first = Rory| last = Smith| title = Chelsea's £40 million bid for Liverpool striker Fernando Torres is an act of desperation| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/liverpool/8287671/Chelseas-40-million-bid-for-Liverpool-striker-Fernando-Torres-is-an-act-of-desperation.html| newspaper = The Daily Telegraph| location = 倫敦| date = 2011-01-27| accessdate = 2011-02-06| archive-date = 2020-10-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201023225607/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/liverpool/8287671/Chelseas-40-million-bid-for-Liverpool-striker-Fernando-Torres-is-an-act-of-desperation.html| dead-url = no}}</ref> 隨後他向利物浦遞交了正式的轉會申請，在第二天也遭到了紅軍方面的拒絕，<ref name="Quotes of the Week: 'Fernando Torres Tonight Submitted A Transfer Request', Wolfsburg Offer Volkswagens For Schulz And Adriano Galliani Is The New Moggi & More">{{Cite news| first = Subhankar| last = Mondal| title = Quotes of the Week: 'Fernando Torres Tonight Submitted A Transfer Request', Wolfsburg Offer Volkswagens For Schulz And Adriano Galliani Is The New Moggi & More| url = http://www.goal.com/en/news/1717/editorial/2011/01/29/2328250/quotes-of-the-week-fernando-torres-tonight-submitted-a| publisher = Goal.com| date = 2011-01-29| accessdate = 2011-02-06| archive-date = 2020-10-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201022064718/https://www.goal.com/en/news/1717/editorial/2011/01/29/2328250/quotes-of-the-week-fernando-torres-tonight-submitted-a| dead-url = no}}</ref> 但托雷斯仍然在同年1月31日轉會至切爾西並與藍戰士簽下一份五年半的合約，據報導，這次的轉會費高達5,000萬英鎊，更打破了英國本土的轉會費紀錄以及令托雷斯成為當地史上第六名昂貴身價的球員。<ref name="Torres makes record move from Liverpool to Chelsea">{{Cite news| title = Torres makes record move from Liverpool to Chelsea| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/9380389.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-01-31| accessdate = 2011-07-27| archive-date = 2020-11-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201122224244/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/9380389.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯於2011年2月6日首次為切爾西上陣，對手正是老東家利物浦，該場比賽切尔西最終以0-1告負。<ref name="Chelsea 0-1 Liverpool">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Chelsea 0–1 Liverpool| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9385584.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-02-06| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archive-date = 2020-10-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020215915/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9385584.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 在2011年4月24日，托雷斯在對[[西漢姆聯足球俱樂部|西漢姆聯]]的英超賽事中射入自己轉會到切爾西以來首個入球，並結束持續了903分鐘的入球荒，也協助藍軍以3:0大勝對手。<ref name="Chelsea 3-0 West Ham">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Chelsea 3–0 West Ham| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9462715.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-04-23| accessdate = 2011-04-24| archive-date = 2020-10-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201019033358/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/9462715.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 這也是他在2010–11賽季為切爾西打進的唯一一個進球，他在這賽季為藍軍上陣18次。<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2010/2011"/>
==== 2011-12球季 ====
[[File:Fernando_Torres_&_Pedro_Poenca.jpg|thumb]]在[[2012年歐洲冠軍聯賽決賽|2012年歐洲冠軍聯賽決賽]]上陣]]
因為托雷斯在發揮一種凌厲的串連作用，再加上他願意做出大量的跑動從而在空中進行搶奪皮球的行動，令他在2011年8月14日作客0:0戰平[[斯托克城足球俱樂部|斯托克城]]的賽事中首發上陣。<ref name="Stoke 0-0 Chelsea">{{Cite news| first = Alistair| last = Magowan| title = Stoke 0–0 Chelsea| url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14435069| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-08-14| accessdate = 2012-03-19| archive-date = 2013-10-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131008103557/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14435069| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他在2011年9月18日作客曼聯的聯賽賽事中打進自己在這個賽季的第一個以及在切爾西的第二個進球，但仍然以1:3不敵紅魔。<ref name="Man Utd 3-1 Chelsea">{{Cite news| first = Phil| last = McNulty| title = Man Utd 3–1 Chelsea| url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14869914| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-09-18| accessdate = 2012-03-19| archive-date = 2013-05-14| archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6GbuSDUpm?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14869914| dead-url = no}}</ref>其後，他在切爾西主場4:1大勝[[斯旺西城足球俱樂部|斯旺西城]]的比賽中打進在這個賽季的第二個聯賽進球。<ref name="Chelsea 4-1 Swansea">{{Cite news| first = Aled| last = Williams| title = Chelsea 4–1 Swansea| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/14957961.stm| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-09-24| accessdate = 2011-09-25| archive-date = 2016-01-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160109084648/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/14957961.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 但在他進球後十分後，他以雙腳飛剷對方球員[[Mark_Gower|Mark Gower]]，令他被主裁判以紅牌罰離場。這也是他在英超的首張紅牌，也導致他停賽三場。<ref name="First red card">{{Cite news| first = Pascal| last = Lemesre| title = Fernando Torres handed red card after scoring| url = http://www.sportsmole.co.uk/football/chelsea/news/torres-handed-red-card-after-scoring_4229.html| publisher = Sportsmole| date = 2011-09-24| accessdate = 2011-09-24| archive-date = 2013-05-12| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130512033648/http://www.sportsmole.co.uk/football/chelsea/news/torres-handed-red-card-after-scoring_4229.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Fernando Torres: Chelsea start has been 'very, very difficult'">{{Cite news| title = Fernando Torres: Chelsea start has been 'very, very difficult'| url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2011/sep/26/fernando-torres-red-card-chelsea| newspaper = 衛報| location = 倫敦| date = 2011-09-26| accessdate = 2013-04-12| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111206104603/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2011/sep/26/fernando-torres-red-card-chelsea| archivedate = 2011-12-06| dead-url = no}}</ref> 2011年10月19日，托雷斯在歐洲冠軍聯賽面對[[KRC亨克|亨克]]的賽事中個人梅開二度，協助俱樂部以5:0大勝對手，這也是他自[[2008–09年欧洲冠军联赛|2008–09賽季歐洲冠軍聯賽]]八強對陣切爾西以來首場歐冠聯賽。<ref name="Chelsea 5-0 Genk">{{Cite news| first = Stephan| last = Shemilt| title = Chelsea 5–0 Genk| url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15269495| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2011-10-19| accessdate = 2012-03-19| archive-date = 2013-08-23| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130823000010/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/15269495| dead-url = no}}</ref><!-- His next Chelsea goals came after scoring twice and also assisting two others against [[Football_League_Championship|Championship]] side [[Leicester_City_F.C.|Leicester City]] in an FA Cup [[2011–12_FA_Cup|quarter-final]] on 18 March 2012, ending a goal drought that stretched 24 games.<ref name="Chelsea 5-2 Leicester">{{Cite news| first = Graham| last = Chase| title = Chelsea 5–2 Leicester| url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17330279| publisher = BBC體育| date = 2012-03-18| accessdate = 2012-03-19}}</ref> On 31 March 2012, Torres scored his first Premier League goal since 24 September 2011, against Aston Villa in a 4–2 away win.<ref name="Games played by Fernando Torres in 2011/2012"/>-->

