== 個人生活 ==
[[File:Fernando_Torres_01_Chelsea_vs_AS-Roma_10AUG2013.jpg|thumb]]

托雷斯的雙親名為José Torres和Flori Sanz，他也有兩名比他大的哥哥和姊姊，Israel (生於1977)和María Paz (生於1976).<ref name="Fernando Torres Sanz">{{cite web| title = Fernando Torres Sanz| url = http://www.nndb.com/people/986/000044854/| publisher = NNDB| accessdate = 2010-07-11| archive-date = 2020-08-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200810024735/https://nndb.com/people/986/000044854/| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托利斯為人低調，2009年5月27日與青梅竹馬的女朋友Olalla Domínguez在馬德里一間位處偏僻的教堂El Escorial舉行私人婚禮，當時只有兩名賓客在場。與很多球星不同，二人早於小時便相戀。事實上托利斯對於感情生活極之低調，亦少有傳出緋聞。<ref name="Football is a funny ol game">{{Cite news| title = Football is a funny ol game| url = http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/article1041158.ece| newspaper = 太陽報| location = 倫敦| date = 2008-04-15| accessdate = 2009-01-13| archive-date = 2014-07-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140713064800/https://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/showbiz/bizarre/article1041158.ece| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Se casa Fernando Torres">{{Cite news| first = Mábel| last = Galaz| title = Se casa Fernando Torres| url = http://elpais.com/elpais/2009/05/28/actualidad/1243493331_850215.html| newspaper = El País| location = Madrid| date = 2009-05-28| accessdate = 2012-03-19| language = es| archive-date = 2020-10-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201018080254/https://elpais.com/elpais/2009/05/28/actualidad/1243493331_850215.html| dead-url = no}}</ref> 兩人在2001年便成為情侶，坊間認為兩人在[[加利西亚_(西班牙)|加利西亚]]的海邊小鎮認識，因為每年托雷斯都會與家人正離開馬德里到當地到假。.<ref name="Fernando Torres welcomes baby 'Leo' after dodging Liverpool match at wife Olalla's bedside">{{Cite news| title = Fernando Torres welcomes baby 'Leo' after dodging Liverpool match at wife Olalla's bedside| url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1336449/Fernando-Torres-welcomes-baby-Leo-Liverpool-strikers-wife-Olalla-gives-birth.html| newspaper = 每日郵報| location = 倫敦| date = 2010-12-07| accessdate = 2010-12-19| archive-date = 2020-04-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421050351/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1336449/Fernando-Torres-welcomes-baby-Leo-Liverpool-strikers-wife-Olalla-gives-birth.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>兩人婚後育有兩名子女。長女Nora於2009年7月8日出生在[[聖地亞哥-德孔波斯特拉|聖地亞哥-德孔波斯特拉]]的La Rosaleda醫院，<ref name="Liverpool star Fernando Torres becomes a dad">{{cite news| title = Liverpool star Fernando Torres becomes a dad| url = http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Liverpool-star-Fernando-Torres-becomes-a-dad-article36989.html| newspaper = Daily Mirror| location = London| date = 2009-07-10| accessdate = 2011-05-18| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130513045114/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Liverpool-star-Fernando-Torres-becomes-a-dad-article36989.html| archivedate = 2013-05-13| dead-url = yes}}</ref> 幼子Leo則於2010年12月6日出生。當時效力利物浦的托利斯為了迎接兒子而前往利物浦當地的醫院，缺席了對[[阿士東維拉|阿士東維拉]]的賽事。<ref>{{Cite news| title = Liverpool 3–0 Aston Villa| url = http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/media-watch/liverpool-3-0-aston-villa| publisher = Liverpool F.C| date = 2010-12-06| accessdate = 2012-06-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120918012250/http://www.liverpoolfc.com/news/media-watch/liverpool-3-0-aston-villa| archive-date = 2012-09-18| dead-url = yes}}</ref>

在2009年，有人報告說，托雷斯積累了1400萬英鎊的個人財富。<ref>{{Cite journal
|date=February 2009| title = Balls to the Crunch| journal = FourFourTwo| page = 50}}</ref> 他曾經在西班牙搖滾樂隊[[El_Canto_del_Loco|El Canto del Loco]]的MV"Ya nada volverá a ser como antes"裡出現，<ref name="Fernando Torres (V)">{{cite web| title = Fernando Torres (V)| url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1895576/| publisher = Internet Movie Database| accessdate = 2010-06-20| archive-date = 2021-03-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210303063606/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1895576/| dead-url = no}}</ref> 托雷斯與樂隊中的主唱[[Dani_Martín|Dani Martín]]是好友，透過此次影片向大眾傳達與這名足球員友好的關係。<ref name="Dani Martín">{{Cite news| title = Dani Martín| url = http://www.fernando9torres.com/index.php?s=charlacon&id=11| publisher = Fernando Torres| date = 2005-09-30| accessdate = 2010-06-20| language = es| archive-date = 2020-10-19| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201019063216/http://www.fernando9torres.com/index.php?s=charlacon&id=11| dead-url = no}}</ref> 他曾經在2005年的喜劇電影「托倫特3：保護者」(''Torrente 3: El protector'')客串出現。<ref name="Full cast and crew for Torrente 3: El protector">{{cite web| title = Full cast and crew for Torrente 3: El protector| url = http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0444505/fullcredits| publisher = Internet Movie Database| accessdate = 2010-06-20| archive-date = 2020-04-21| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200421050414/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0444505/fullcredits| dead-url = no}}</ref> 在2009年，他推出了一個名為「托雷斯: 聖嬰: 我的故事」(''Torres: El Niño: My Story'')的自傳。<ref name="El Nino: My Story">{{Cite news| first = Simon| last = Wilson| title = El Nino: My Story| url = http://espnfc.com/feature?id=688190&cc=5739| publisher = ESPN FC| date = 2009-10-02| accessdate = 2013-04-11| archive-date = 2013-06-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130606134409/http://espnfc.com/feature?id=688190&cc=5739| dead-url = no}}</ref>
托雷斯也是作家[[J·R·R·托尔金|J·R·R·托尔金]]的忠實支持者，而他也弄了一個[[Tengwar|Tengwar]]字款的"Fernando"在左前臀上。<ref>{{cite web|title=Famous Tolkien and Lord of the Ring fans|url=http://www.tolkienlibrary.com/press/1010-Famous_Tolkien_fans.php|publisher=Tolkien Library|accessdate=2013-07-04|archive-date=2013-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730185138/http://www.tolkienlibrary.com/press/1010-Famous_Tolkien_fans.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

